ZH: 这个地方的泥土非常肥沃。
EN: The soil in this place is very fertile.

ZH: 这块泥土适合种花。
EN: This patch of soil is suitable for planting flowers.

ZH: 农民们正在耕种泥土。
EN: The farmers are cultivating the soil.

ZH: 孩子们在田地里玩泥土。
EN: The children are playing with the soil in the field.

ZH: 泥土中含有很多养分。
EN: Soil contains a lot of nutrients.

ZH: 我们需要用泥土来覆盖种子。
EN: We need to cover the seeds with soil.

ZH: 这片泥土需要浇水才能保持湿润。
EN: This patch of soil needs to be watered to keep it moist.

ZH: 前几天的暴雨把泥土冲走了。
EN: The heavy rain a few days ago washed away the soil.

ZH: 泥土对植物生长起着重要作用。
EN: Soil plays an important role in plant growth.

ZH: 这块土地上的泥土很稀薄。
EN: The soil on this piece of land is very thin.

ZH: 这片山区的泥土比较贫瘠。
EN: The soil in this mountainous area is relatively barren.

ZH: 我们需要挖掘更深的泥土才能找到水。
EN: We need to dig deeper into the soil to find water.

ZH: 种植不同种类的植物能改善泥土质量。
EN: Planting different types of plants can improve the quality of the soil.

ZH: 他们用泥土建造了一个小屋。
EN: They built a small house with mud and soil.

ZH: 他们混合泥土和水来制作陶器。
EN: They mix soil and water to make pottery.

ZH: 这种泥土非常适合制作砖块。
EN: This type of soil is perfect for making bricks.

ZH: 他们用泥土筑起了一道围墙。
EN: They built a around wall with soil.

ZH: 这片泥土被雨水冲刷得很干净。
EN: The rain washed away the soil in this area.

ZH: 这块泥土可以用来垒土坝。
EN: This mound of soil can be used to build a dirt dam.

ZH: 在种植时要选择合适的泥土。
EN: It is important to choose the right type of soil for planting.
